<p>NOTICE OF FUNDING OPPORTUNITY: LAW ENFORCEMENT, PROSECUTION, AND COUNTY COURT APPOINTED SPECIAL ADVOCATE-BASED VICTIM ASSISTANCE PROGRAMS</p>
<p>The Illinois Criminal Justice Information Authority is requesting applications for funding to support law enforcement, prosecution, and county court appointed special advocate-based victim assistance programs.</p>
<p><a href="https://grants.icjia.cloud/grants/20170824vocacourts">Click here for application materials, funding eligibility, and other information.</a></p>
<p><strong>Application deadline: October 15, 2017</strong></p>
